title: D-Day: The King Who Fooled Hitler
actors: Richard J. Aldrich, Rory Cormac, Helen McCrory, Peter Sullivan
plot: In a tale of double agents and decoys, this documentary reveals, for the first time, the story of King George VI's elaborate ruse to divert German attention away from the Normandy landings in 1944.
name: D-Day: The King Who Fooled Hitler
